Hello i Have A Question

Lets Say i want to Design A Dynamic Component That i want To Use Multiple Times With Different Purposes. for example i have a details component that its view is different for invoice detail and transaction detail what is the best way to dynamic it ?

1. dynamic it with multiple Input Variable And Code Like this.
class {
@Input() myvar: boolean = false
}

template {
<div *ngIf="myvar"></div>
<img *ngIf="myvar"></div>
<span *ngIf="!myvar"></div>
}

2. dynamic it with two different views and load them when we want use each

class {
@Input() myvar: boolean = false
}

template {
<div>
{{(myvar) ? invoiceView : transactionView}}
</div>

<ng-template #invoiceView>
//some code about invoice View
</ng-template>

<ng-template #transactionView>
//some code about transaction View
</ng-template>

}
